{"type": "article", "id": 24078, "title": "印出树影的窗帘", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-18T07:00:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 109, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702133513xQk3MpTgfIJeRtAV.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一款丝制的窗帘，在阳光的照射下窗帘本身印出了自然的光影，通过深浅来区分，就像花草树木的影子印在了窗帘上，非常漂亮。窗帘整体是紫色的，上面混合了一些蓝色或黄色，带给人更丰富的变化的自然。设计师来自美国新泽西，这是他的第二代，<a href=\"http://www.louierigano.com/Shadow-Curtains\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133511W5F0Kiq13xefjGoE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021335120AMRX3kjm8DQV5fp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133512RHdSgqPWG7CiM1YD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021335134Q2HPhpygU7ex5c3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}